<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About</title>
    <style>
        /* Gaya dasar untuk body */
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6a11cb, #2575fc);
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        /* Gaya untuk kontainer */
        .container {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 40px;
            width: 80%;
            max-width: 600px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            text-align: center;
            animation: fadeIn 1s ease;
        }

        /* Animasi fade-in */
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-20px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        h1 {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 2em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        /* Gaya untuk teks paragraf */
        p {
            color: #555;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        /* Gaya untuk form */
        form {
            text-align: left;
        }

        label {
            display: block;
            color: #333;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }

        input[type="text"],
        input[type="file"],
        textarea {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            margin-top: 5px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 1em;
        }

        textarea {
            resize: vertical;
            min-height: 100px;
        }

        /* Gaya untuk kontainer tombol */
        .button-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        /* Gaya tombol submit */
        button,
        .button-container a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: white;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6a11cb, #2575fc);
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 1em;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: background 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        button:hover,
        .button-container a:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #5d0eb3, #1e63cc);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>About Us</h1>
        <p>Selamat datang di halaman About. Di sini, Anda dapat mengetahui lebih banyak tentang kami dan apa yang kami lakukan.</p>
        <p>Ini adalah proyek sederhana untuk memahami lebih dalam tentang manajemen file dan pengembangan web.</p>

        <!-- Form untuk mengisi nama, deskripsi, dan upload file -->
        <form action="/upload" method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data">
            <label for="name">Nama:</label>
            <input type="text" id="name" name="name" placeholder="Masukkan nama Anda" required>

            <label for="description">Deskripsi:</label>
            <textarea id="description" name="description" placeholder="Tuliskan deskripsi Anda..." required></textarea>

            <label for="file">Upload File (Max 3GB):</label>
            <input type="file" id="file" name="file" accept=".pdf,.doc,.docx,.txt" required>

            <div class="button-container">
                <button type="submit">Submit</button>
                <a href="/">Kembali ke Home</a>
            </div>
        </form>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 